e fudge."<br><br><br> Me: Also I haven't said that as lev 59 I couldn't do it, but my point was that<br>lev 45 character can not  do Forager/hunter spawn as you said it could. Also<br>if you have lev 1 tracker at the zone line, he can just tell you what mob is<br>up, so what if you know that Doom is up, you lev 45 character needs to find<br>and kill the mob. Lets say you go to do this with paladin, he cant track mob<br>down, and even if he stumbles over the mob (hoping all this green trash that<br>still can do some damage to lev 45 character doesnt kill him first) does, he<br>can't solo it. Thats at least one part of your claim that is wrong.<br><br>(Addenum: This is the part when car dealer tells you WTF, so if you car doesnt have AC as I promised, you still have Warranty and stereo)<br>PL Guy: OK so because you find one perceived inaccuracy, the entire guide is worthless now right, and you want your money back? BS (stands for BULLSHIT), it ain't (is not) gonna happen.  Methinks (I think) you were looking for something that would allow you to sit your ass (gluteous maximus) in Freeport and just sit there and make 1K per hour every hour with no effort.  There are no such methods.<br><br><br><br>Me: Please feel free to reply to either of my 2 e-mails and spell that acronym<br>for me.<br><br>PF Guys: Once again, so there can be no misunderstanding, it stands for "what the fuck."  Feel free to e-mail me again if you forget it and need me to remind you.<br> <br>Regards,<br> <br>Doug Reding<br>www.powerleveling.com<br><br>
