take. <br><br>I mean just look at it, you are claiming that level 45 paladin/rogue/warrior CAN solo lev 45 mob, or even level 50 named mob that spawns after that? (i used those 3 classes because with them it is most obvious that this system doesnt work as promissed, not even close to that 99% )<br><br>And I am the one that has been called names and that I dont know what I am talking about. <br><br>Also seller addmited that for some of those mobs i might need help, but do you see that in his auction? <br><br>I have said this in e-mail and I will say it again:<br><br>You made wrong claim in your auction, and I want  refund for it, no more no less. You promised that as level 45 I will be able to do this cycle and it simply is not doable, and thats why I want refund.<br><br>I hope this makes whole situation clearer.<br><br>
